@Node CmdLineOptions "CmdLineOptions"

  Command Line Options
  ====================

    When no system options are specified they are as follows:

      Command Line Arguments (argv[x])
      --------------------------------

      2  <confnum>

      3  <diz_file> (full filename and path)

      4  <file_name> (no path)

      5  [NOUSER]


